      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'm so sorry you're feeling this way, but I'm here for you. Sometimes things may not run as we hoped, and it is okay to feel down during such times. This emptiness you're feeling is not visible to anyone else, and does not mean there's nothing left for you to create or to explore. I urge you to reach out to those around you or seek professional help, as there is always support out there for someone in your situation. Remember, every ending is a new beginning in disguise. Allow yourself to grieve your loss, but don't forget to try to love yourself better along the way.",
